  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc7 \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "India will supply fuel only if Srilanka gives advance payment",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to those who know about the matter, India has said that if it has to provide fuel to Sri Lanka, advance payment should be made while the loans given to Sri Lanka have ended.",
        "India has stopped supplying gas and diesel to Sri Lanka, which is facing its worst economic crisis, as it has run out of dollars to buy gas and fuel, and India has delayed sending some ships until the Sri Lankan Petroleum Corporation provides the money, Indian officials said on condition of anonymity.",
        "A Twitter post by Minister Kanchanavijaisekara revealed that four fuel tankers from the Government of India's Oil Refining Corporation are waiting to confirm the advance payment.",
        "Sri Lanka is expecting a fresh loan of $500 million from India to buy fuel, with its foreign exchange reserves completely depleted.",
        "Sri Lanka has sent representatives to the country to buy oil from Qatar, and it is also seeking oil from Russia.",
        "A spokesman for the Indian Oil Corporation said that it has supplied 450,000 tonnes of fuel to the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation during the period from March to June."
      ],
